        <item>
            <title>新 Tesla Model 3 Performance 抵港　破百 3.1 秒 +  528KM 续航力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-model-3-performance-press-release</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:59:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insane Mode]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Performance]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纯电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231986</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日 Tesla 发布全新 Model 3 Performance 电动车，里里外外均有升级，0-100 km/h 加速更仅需 3.1 秒。以新「一换一」计划计算，意向价为 $396,880 港币。今日 Tesla 邀请了小编去看看 Tesla Model 3 Performance ，现在就带大家欣赏这款全新热门电动车。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新<span lang="EN-US"> Model 3 Performance </span>进行了内外部的升级，包括全新可调较自动适应减震系统、全新高效能 <span lang="EN-US">Mode<wbr />l 3 </span>摩打，<span lang="EN-US">0-100 km/h </span>加速只需<span lang="EN-US"> 3.1 </span>秒，最高时速可达 261 公里每小时，最高续航距离（WLTP）可达 528 公里。Model 3 Performance 配备带有<span lang="EN-US"> Performance </span>标志的通风<span lang="EN-US"> Sport </span>座椅、碳纤维尾翼和碳纤维内饰等，增强整体驾乘体验，由 5 月 1 日起可于全线<span lang="EN-US"> Tesla </span>体验中心参观。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232343" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><p style="text-align: center;">▲Performance 独有标志</p><h2>全新可调校自动适应减震系统 + Insane Mode</h2><p>Tesla Model 3 Performance 新增以软件主导的可调校自动适应减震系统，能够提升悬挂系统缓冲表现，有效减低路面对汽车的冲击之余，亦可保持车辆转向灵活。Model 3 Performance 亦是第一款设有「Insane Mode」的 Model 3 系列电车。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲首次于 Model 3 加入 Insane Mode</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-price-reduce-2024-april/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 香港车价下调万六元　Model 3 RWD 新一换一价 25.4 万</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 与百度将达成协议　协助 Tesla FSD 进入中国市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/elon-musk-visit-china-2024/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 访华与李强会面   Tesla 全数通过中国汽车数据安全要求</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Performance 高性能煞车制动、底盘</h2><p>根据厂方资料显示，Model 3 Performance 配备更大的煞车碟、卡钳及高性能刹车制动片，在任何速度都能够提供强大制动力及一致的刹车体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232287" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Tesla Model 3 Performance 卡钳</p><h2>锻造 Performance 轮圈</h2><p>Model 3 Performance 标准配置新设计的 20 吋 Warp 版车轮，为驾驶者提供更清晰的转向反馈，提升续航力及舒适度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲Model 3 Performance 标准配置 20 吋 Warp 版车轮</p><h2>通风 Sport 座椅</h2><p>全新设计的 Performance 前排座椅带有 Performance 标志，配备升级版座垫支撑包覆感更强，并且提供通风及暖感功能，为用家提供更一体化的乘坐体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232325" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲前排座椅有 Performance 标志</p><h2>碳纤维细节</h2><p>Model 3 Performance 加入了不少碳纤维元素，提升车辆「跑味」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲碳纤维内饰</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲碳纤维尾翼</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-price-reduce-2024-april/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 香港车价下调万六元　Model 3 RWD 新一换一价 25.4 万</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 与百度将达成协议　协助 Tesla FSD 进入中国市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/elon-musk-visit-china-2024/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 访华与李强会面   Tesla 全数通过中国汽车数据安全要求</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>全新前后扰流设计</h2><p>为突显 Model 3 Performance 的性能，Tesla 采用了不少跑车味浓的设计，例如全新的前后扰流及头唇设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲全新头唇</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232339" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲有效降低风阻的前扰流</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232368" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲后扰流设计</p><h2>Model 3 Performance Dual-Motor 规格</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">加速（0-100 公里／小时）</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">3.1 秒</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">最高时速</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">261 公里／小时</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">续航距离（WLTP 标准）</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">528 公里</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">车轮</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">20&#8243; Warp 车轮</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">座位配置</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">5</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">尺寸</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 100%;">高度： 1,431 毫米</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">宽度： 1,933 毫米</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">长度： 4,724 毫米</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">重量</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">1,854 公斤</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">容量</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">682 公升</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">基本配置</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;"><ul><li style="text-align: left;">15.4 吋中央触控萤幕及 8 吋后触控式萤幕</li><li style="text-align: left;">可调节电动前排座椅</li><li style="text-align: left;">前排通风及暖感座椅；后排暖感座椅</li><li style="text-align: left;">自订环境灯</li><li style="text-align: left;">3 个 USB 插口和手机无线充电（可为 2 部智能电话充电）</li><li style="text-align: left;">电热軚盘</li><li style="text-align: left;">全车双层隔音玻璃</li><li style="text-align: left;">专享网络（30 天免费）</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">高级音响</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">15 个喇叭和双重低音喇叭<br />
